00:18:39,160 --> 00:18:43,581
What do you know...about that boy?!

261
00:18:46,918 --> 00:18:50,129
There is something important which

262
00:18:50,213 --> 00:18:52,215
that boy wants to prove and
protect even if it costs him his life.

263
00:18:54,592 --> 00:18:57,053
I'd like to prove that I can become
a respectable Ninja

264
00:18:57,554 --> 00:19:00,473
even though I can't use
Ninjutsu and Genjutsu!

265
00:19:01,266 --> 00:19:03,226
That would be the ultimate for me!

266
00:19:04,060 --> 00:19:05,562
That's why I...

267
00:19:05,645 --> 00:19:08,648
wanted to make him a man
that could protect that thing.

268
00:19:09,607 --> 00:19:10,942
That's all there is...

269
00:19:12,569 --> 00:19:16,656
Lee!
