272
00:19:20,618 --> 00:19:23,413
Yippie, yeah! Yippie yeah!

273
00:19:23,496 --> 00:19:26,875
Lee, listen to my explanation
seriously, all right?!

274
00:19:29,294 --> 00:19:30,879
Y-Yes, Sensei!

275
00:19:30,962 --> 00:19:33,214
Let me first say that...

276
00:19:33,298 --> 00:19:36,217
this is more of a forbidden Jutsu
than the Primary Lotus!

277
00:19:36,718 --> 00:19:40,096
And it will become the
most special technique for you.

278
00:19:41,639 --> 00:19:43,057
Special...?

279
00:19:43,141 --> 00:19:44,601
However...

280
00:19:44,684 --> 00:19:50,064
there is one strict condition
for using this technique.

281
00:19:50,899 --> 00:19:52,025
That is...

282
00:19:54,694 --> 00:19:55,987
That is...

283
00:20:01,576 --> 00:20:02,702
What?

284
00:20:03,328 --> 00:20:06,164
I don't know what you're planning to do...

285
00:20:06,915 --> 00:20:09,459
dut this is the end for you.

286
00:20:09,542 --> 00:20:10,752
That's true...

287
00:20:12,337 --> 00:20:15,423
In any case...
it will be the end with the next.

288
00:20:16,591 --> 00:20:20,345
Neji...Sasuke...and...

289
00:20:24,140 --> 00:20:28,227
There is no way that I alone
can lose in a place like this!

290
00:20:30,021 --> 00:20:33,650
Guy Sensei...please allow this...!

291
00:20:34,692 --> 00:20:35,944
It is now!

292
00:20:47,038 --> 00:20:51,167
The time to carry through and
protect one's own Way of the Ninja!

293
00:20:52,126 --> 00:20:54,504
The Third Gate of Life...open!

294
00:21:05,723 --> 00:21:10,269
Hey, can you hear it?

295
00:21:10,353 --> 00:21:14,691
The clear, blue sky

296
00:21:14,774 --> 00:21:19,487
goes on and on

297
00:21:19,570 --> 00:21:23,783
The ocean

298
00:21:23,866 --> 00:21:28,621
spans limitlessly

299
00:21:28,705 --> 00:21:32,959
Please keep that smile

300
00:21:33,042 --> 00:21:37,797
on your face forever

301
00:21:37,880 --> 00:21:43,261
Or else I'll cry

302
00:21:43,344 --> 00:21:47,265
You won't have to search around you

303
00:21:47,348 --> 00:21:51,269
It's all ok now.

304
00:21:51,352 --> 00:21:56,691
Everyone is inside

305
00:21:56,774 --> 00:22:00,069
this hand

306
00:22:00,153 --> 00:22:05,241
When you want to cry,
and you want to run away

307
00:22:05,324 --> 00:22:09,787
When you forget what happiness is

308
00:22:09,871 --> 00:22:13,833
Just sing.

309
00:22:13,916 --> 00:22:18,963
Light is born, and darkness was born

310
00:22:19,047 --> 00:22:21,215
The two are one

311
00:22:21,299 --> 00:22:28,056
Harmonia, feel the telepathy

312
00:22:28,139 --> 00:22:34,145
Hey, can you hear it?

313
00:22:37,482 --> 00:22:41,152
Effort is always rewarded.
My belief in this has brought me this far.

314
00:22:42,195 --> 00:22:45,114
Neji, Sasuke, and Naruto...

315
00:22:45,198 --> 00:22:48,785
There's no way that I can lose
in a place like this!

316
00:22:48,868 --> 00:22:50,870
Even though this technique is
my ace in the hole,

317
00:22:50,953 --> 00:22:52,789
